overview: Atsushi Onita announced that FMW-E will have the best explosion match ever.  It was decided that this match would be called the "Death Match of Hell":  - Barbed wire barricade landmines explosion x8  - Barbed wire rope explosion x2  - Barbed wire baseball bat explosion x2  - A new weapon: The Table Explosion  Card:  Fake Explosion Match:  Yumehito Imanari vs. Buatsushi Futonita  Six Man Tag Team Match:  HASEGAWA, Naoshi Sano & Yuichi Taniguchi vs. Monster Leather, Mr. Atomic & Toshiya Kawarai  Tag Team Match:  Gabai Ji-chan & Kikutaro vs. Brahman Brothers (Brahamn Kei & Brahman Shu)  Throwing Money Bunkhouse Three Way Death Match:  Miss Mongol vs. Drew Parker vs. Nene Dai  Barbed Wire Explosion Six Man Tag Team Death Match:  Atsushi Onita, Minory Fujita & Ricky Fuji vs. Abdullah Kobayashi, Onryo & Yuko Miyamoto
title: FMW-E: Independence Day
